Hook continued to clutch his arm, and got to his knees. "Please my lord,
if I was healthy I would not have disobeyed." he pleaded, crawling
towards Havotron.

Spinister looked to Needlenose, then motioned for him to move back,
before he disapeared from his friends sight, just vanishing into thin
air.
